    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project lovers! This vehicle is looking for a new owner who isn't afraid to get their hands dirty and bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical work and some cosmetic TLC, it offers a fantastic, budget-friendly opportunity for someone looking for a rewarding restoration project or a reliable source of parts!",
